'''Kushitama-hime-no-Mikoto Shrine''' (櫛玉比女命神社) is a [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] located in [[:en:Kōryō, Nara|Hirogawa Town]], [[:en:Kitakatsuragi District, Nara|Kitakatsuragi District]], [[:en:Nara Prefecture|Nara Prefecture]].
It is listed as a {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|2=ja|3=式内社|qq=draft|1=Shikinaisha|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikinaisha|13=User:Immanuelle|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|lt=Shikinaisha}} and was formerly classified as a {{ill|Village Shrine|ja|村社|lt=Son-sha|1=Modern_system_of_ranked_Shinto_shrines#Village_shrines|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Village Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度}}. The shrine is situated atop the {{ill|Kushitama-hime Shrine Kofun|ja|櫛玉媛神社古墳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kushitama-hime Shrine Kofun|qq=}}, an ancient Kofun that remains unexcavated.<ref group="Note">The kofun has not been surveyed.</ref>
== Deity == The enshrined deity is {{ill|Kushitama-hime-no-Mikoto|ja|櫛玉比女命|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kushitama-hime-no-Mikoto|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}.<ref>Hirose District Shrine Registry</ref>
It is said that she is {{ill|Miketsu-hime-no-Mikoto|ja|御炊屋姫命|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miketsu-hime-no-Mikoto|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ミカシキヤヒメ}}, the consort of {{ill|Kushitama Nigihayahi-no-Mikoto|ja|櫛玉饒速日命|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kushitama Nigihayahi-no-Mikoto|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ニギハヤヒ}}.<ref>Shrine notice board</ref>
== Auxiliary Shrines (Sessha) == * **Benzaiten Shrine** (祭神: {{ill|Ichikishima-hime-no-Mikoto|ja|市杵島姫命|1=Ichikishima-hime|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikishima-hime-no-Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikishima-hime|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to イチキシマヒメ}})
